info.author: Sam Clegg
info.description:
pypod is a python library and script for managing iPod
metadata and music files.  It is similar in scope to
gnupod (written in perl) and is designed to work well
with other programs that generate iPod metadata such
as gtktop and gnupod.
info.name: pypod
info.summary: tools for working with the Apple iPod
